id: "class:magus#kensai"
name: "Kensai"
description: "A kensai spends his life focusing his training and meditation into a\
  \ rapturous perfection of the use of a single weapon, which is usually but not always\
  \ a sword, channeling his arcane might through it in a dizzying and deadly dance\
  \ beyond the abilities of even the greatest of mundane warriors."
